      <media:content height="1799" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2026/03/29/fashion/26CAROLE-RADZIWILL-01-jkhm/26CAROLE-RADZIWILL-01-jkhm-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg" width="1800"></media:content>
      <media:credit>Lucia Bell-Epstein for The New York Times</media:credit>
      <media:description>Rebutting others’ accounts of her deceased loved ones — her husband, Anthony Radziwill; his cousin, John F. Kennedy, Jr.; and Carolyn Bessette Kennedy — has long been something of a duty for Carole Radziwill. But even as she has readily taken up that cause, she is also tired of doing it.</media:description>
